###top is a command in linux which is used to check all your process id 
[root@ip-172-31-115-189 ~]$ docker top mongo
UID                 PID                 PPID                C                   STIME               TTY                 TIME                CMD
lxd                 8088                8065                2                   08:45               ?                   00:00:00            mongod --bind_ip_all
